The paper discusses the threats to privacy infrastructures, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). It also touches upon the topic of cybersecurity (cs.CY) as it discusses the misuse of privacy infrastructures by attackers. The paper also discusses the need for further research to mitigate the risks, which falls under the category of software engineering (cs.SE) and system and information theory (cs.SI). Finally, the paper discusses the Tor network, which falls under the category of distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC).
